<plot>Solongo is a Mongolian expatriate living in Seoul with her American husband. Myungjin, recently returned to her native country after 10 years abroad studying painting, feels equally displaced. Through the mysterious connection of a 10 year old girl riding past on a kick scooter, the two women find unexpected solace and hope for the future as they confront the choices they made in their lives.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?237429</url></doc>
